The benchmarks in this folder are CML versions of a subset of the benchmarks
from Intel MPI Benchmarks suite. The Intel benchmark suite uses MPI
primitives in the benchmarks. This suite *simulates* the behavior of Intel's
suite with the help of CML primitives.

Intel MPI benchmark suite -------------------------
(http://software.intel.com/en-us/articles/intel-mpi-benchmarks/).

-- kc
